  <brief_title>Polymethyl Methacrylate and (PEGT/PBT) Centralizer by the Uncemented BIHAPRO THP</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 3 Randomised, Prospective Study Comparing the PMMA and the Resorbable PEGT/PBT Centralizer by the Uncemented BIHAPRO Total Hip Prosthesis</official_title>
